<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Just say which direction.Below is a substantially longer, more detailed LaTeX biography, still aimed at a younger (but serious) audience, written to be narrative, ethical, and reflective, and explicitly avoiding discussion of suicide while preserving gravity, war, renunciation, silence, method, music, gendered social worlds, and philosophical development.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">The subject is Ludwig Wittgenstein (mentioned here for reference; do not repeat inside the LaTeX unless you wish).</p>
